<br>
For example Gallenite's Chaos does not stack with Improved Damage IV, but Anger of Druzzil would be used instead of either IDIV or Gallenite's Chaos.<br>
<br>
Summoning haste does not stack with Naki's Pernicity, however when summon haste does not work, the ring will be used instead.<br>
